# Requirement Analysis

## Functional Requirements

- Student enters study-related text.
- Detect emotion using the BiLSTM model.
- Generate personalized AI guidance using Gemini AI.
- Store user interaction history.
- Display analytics dashboard.

## Non-Functional Requirements

- User-friendly interface
- Fast emotion prediction
- Accurate AI responses
- Secure API integration
- Easy deployment using Streamlit

## Software Requirements

- Python
- Streamlit
- TensorFlow
- Keras
- Google Gemini API
- Plotly
- Pandas
- NumPy

## Hardware Requirements

- Windows 10/11
- Minimum 8 GB RAM
- Internet connection
